{"tid":1734000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大律師：警察有權繼續用蒙面法拉市民 ！","createTime":"2019-11-18T08:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T11:29:40.000Z","uid":22556,"like":12,"dislike":448,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"c2c1ed6a42f997b9ef877b2e28b906c64797d245","tid":1734000,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:31:12.000Z","msg":"即使惡法被裁定違憲，並不代表市民在往後遊行集會中蒙面，再無犯法、被捕風險。執業大律師陸偉雄表示，經初步研究判辭後，相信由於《蒙面法》未完全被推翻，警方仍可以《蒙面法》拘捕市民，提醒市民不要掉以輕心。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「前線警察仍有可能拉咗先，等官司有結果再決定告唔告。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n至於已被拘捕人士，陸偉雄表示律政司同樣有可能暫緩處理案件，待司法覆核案有上訴進一步結果後，方再作檢控決定。<br />\n<br />\n問到案件下一步走向，陸偉雄指今次只是首次判決，相信律政司會不滿今次判決上訴：「最終可能上訴至終院。」<br />\n<br />\n【反蒙面惡法】高院裁定《蒙面法》違憲 大律師提醒：勿掉以輕心 | 2019-11-18 | 壹週刊"},{"pid":"abf853cadfa015e318ebbad4f40fbf5f3707cfa8","tid":1734000,"uid":58630,"like":182,"dislike":1,"score":181,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:32:22.000Z","msg":"佢要拉你根本唔洗理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0498c0dbaae2eb8630c399e105a38831303efb61","tid":1734000,"uid":289708,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:33:47.000Z","msg":"誰大誰惡誰正確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159230f3711312ecc477cbac2898c44491b80445","tid":1734000,"uid":171272,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:35:27.000Z","msg":"借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你唔敢去理工救人嘅話...<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1733944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1733944</a>"},{"pid":"6ba9da8973897d6f412ef00e21cdc79931895c03","tid":1734000,"uid":155095,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T08:36:13.000Z","msg":"等人大釋法"},{"pid":"a5d65fd577adceaa6fd9f7b7f52427204d139b87","tid":1734000,"uid":2455,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20